show dbs - shows all databases

show collections - shows all collections at the current database


use <database name> - creates database and switches on to it
		    - swithces to database that exist


db - shows on what current database are you at


db.createUser() - creates a new user for the database on which the method is run


db.createCollection(<collection name>) - creates collection or table if in sql


db.<collection name>.insert({key: value}) - inserts data to selected collection


db.<collection>.find() - gives the list of documents in the current collection


db.<collection>.update({key value pair, the document looking for}, {<update row>})


db.<collection>.remove() - removes that collection